[[有机合成|有机合成]]中常用四氯化钛作路易斯酸。<ref>{{cite book | author= L.-L. Gundersen, F. Rise, K. Undheim  | title= Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis | publisher = J. Wiley & Sons| year=2004| volume=| | chapter = Titanium(IV) chloride|edition =L. Paquette |location= New York}}</ref>

